oai_dc:dc.dc:title: INVENTORY OF THE STABILITY OF EXISTING PLACED BLOCK REVETMENTS IN THE NETHERLANDS
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Stoutjesdijk, Theo
Breteler, Mark Klein
Johanson, Hans
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Netherlands
revetment
revetment stability
block inventory
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This paper describes the results of a nationwide inventory of the stability of existing placed block revetments in the Netherlands. The inventory is now complete at a basic level: the revetments have been tested using simple stability criteria. These criteria are described in this paper and the main results of the inventory are presented and discussed.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 26 (1998): Proceedings of 26th Conference on Coastal Engineering, Copenhagen, Denmark, 1998.
